ally settles the traditionally perceived conflict between observations and\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2009 08:21:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2009 06:52:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-27"}
