 The formalism can be applied also as a postprocessing\noperation, offering all subsequent analytical and computationnal advantages of\nsymmetrization. The specific case of a quantum wire (QWRs) with $C_{3v}$ point\ngroup symmetry is used as a concrete illustration of the application of MSRF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2009 15:01:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2009 08:43:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Mar 2010 16:09:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
